的な支援を通じて着実に水道の更新に努めてまいりたいというふうに思っております。"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/131", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/182", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/184", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/186", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/188", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/195", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/197", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/199", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/201", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/203", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/205", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/207", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/209", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/211", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/217", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/219", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/222", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/290", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/386", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/388", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/390", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/398", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/402", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261